1
00:00:19,544 --> 00:00:21,069
HANK: Stark!

2
00:00:21,464 --> 00:00:22,704
HOWARD: He doesn't seem happy.

3
00:00:22,784 --> 00:00:24,149
Hello, Hank.

4
00:00:25,824 --> 00:00:27,474
