with such ferocity, Dr. Pym.

19
00:01:04,864 --> 00:01:05,990
Ah...

20
00:01:07,104 --> 00:01:09,072
- (GROANS)
- Easy, Hank.

21
00:01:10,424 --> 00:01:13,075
You mention my wife again

22
00:01:13,144 --> 00:01:15,192
and I'll show you ferocity.

23
00:01:15,264 --> 00:01:16,868
Don't look at me. You said it.

24
00:01:17,944 --> 00:01:20,265
I formally tender my resignation.

25
00:01:20,344 --> 00:01:22,665
We don't accept it. Formally.

26
00:01:22,744 --> 00:01:24,030
Hank,

27
00:01:24,104 --> 00:01:25,833
we need you.

28
00:01:25,904 --> 00:01:28,225
The Pym Particle is a miracle. Please.

29
00:01:28,304 --> 00:01:30,625
Don't let your past determine the future.

30
00:01:30,704 --> 00:01:33,628
As long as I am alive,

31
00:01:33,704 --> 00:01:37,186
nobody will ever get that formula.

32
00:01:43,864 --> 00:01:45,866
We shouldn't let him leave the building.

33
00:01:45,944 --> 00:01:48,151
