Thank you. Thank you.

116
00:05:53,383 --> 00:05:55,954
You really stuck it
to those billionaire SOBs.

117
00:05:56,023 --> 00:05:58,549
The more I read about
what you did and stuff...

118
00:05:58,623 --> 00:06:01,149
I'm like, "Wow, I know this guy?

119
00:06:01,223 --> 00:06:03,305
