120
00:06:03,383 --> 00:06:05,750
Well, I'm very happy in this job,

121
00:06:05,863 --> 00:06:08,150
and I really just appreciate
the opportunity to...

122
00:06:08,223 --> 00:06:09,668
Well, you're fired, of course.

123
00:06:12,103 --> 00:06:13,468
I can't really keep you on.

124
00:06:13,543 --> 00:06:15,227
Wait, what? Fired?

125
00:06:15,303 --> 00:06:16,384
Yeah.

126
00:06:16,463 --> 00:06:18,465
Dale, look, it wasn't a violent crime.
I mean, I'm a good worker.

127
00:06:18,583 --> 00:06:21,427
No, it wasn't a violent crime.
It was a cool crime.

128
00:06:21,543 --> 00:06:22,829
I'll tell you what, though.

129
00:06:22,903 --> 00:06:26,066
This will be totally off the books,
off the records,

130
00:06:26,143 --> 00:06:29,147
but if you want to grab one of those
Mango Fruit Blasts

131
00:06:29,223 --> 00:06:30,554
