Trumped-up BS to scare the USSR.

218
00:11:48,462 --> 00:11:52,308
Hank, will you tell our guests
what you told me

219
00:11:52,382 --> 00:11:55,909
every single time I asked you,

220
00:11:57,502 --> 00:11:59,982
"Was the Ant-Man real?"

221
00:12:00,062 --> 00:12:01,712
Just a tall tale.

222
00:12:01,782 --> 00:12:02,829
Right.

223
00:12:02,902 --> 00:12:05,985
Because how could anything
so miraculous possibly be real?

224
00:12:16,422 --> 00:12:20,029
Well, I was inspired by the legend
of the Ant-Man.

225
00:12:20,102 --> 00:12:22,946
And with my breakthrough
shrinking inorganic material,

226
00:12:23,022 --> 00:12:26,071
