to shrink a person?

227
00:12:26,942 --> 00:12:28,546
Could that be done?

228
00:12:29,462 --> 00:12:33,353
Well, it's not a legend anymore.

229
00:12:34,982 --> 00:12:36,702
- (MACHINE WHIRRING)
- Distinguished guests,

230
00:12:37,062 --> 00:12:40,862
I am proud to present
the end of warfare as we know it.

231
00:12:40,942 --> 00:12:42,751
The Yellowjacket!

232
00:12:42,822 --> 00:12:43,948
(WHIRRING)

233
00:12:48,742 --> 00:12:49,868
Oh, no.

234
00:12:49,942 --> 00:12:53,264
The Yellowjacket is an all-purpose
weapon of war

235
00:12:53,782 --> 00:12:56,353
capable of altering the size of the wearer

236
00:12:56,422 --> 00:12:58,504
for the ultimate combat advantage.

237
00:12:59,182 --> 00:13:00,593
MAN: <i>We live in an era</i>

238
00:13:00,662 --> 00:13:02,903
<i>in which the weapons
we use to protect ourselves</i>

239
00:13:02,982 --> 00:13:06,065
<i>are undermined
by constant surveillance.</i>

240
00:13:06,142 --> 00:13:07,871
<i>It's time to return to a simpler age.</i>

241
00:13:08,422 --> 00:13:11,790
<i>One where the powers of freedom
can once again operate openly</i>

242
00:13:11,862 --> 00:13:13,148
<i>to protect their interests.</i>

243
00:13:13,902 --> 00:13:16,064
<i>An all-purpose peace-keeping vessel,</i>

244
00:13:16,142 --> 00:13:18,509
<i>The Yellowjacket
can manage any conflict</i>

245
00:13:18,582 --> 00:13:19,947
<i>on the geopolitical landscape</i>

246
00:13:20,022 --> 00:13:22,104
<i>completely unseen.</i>

247
00:13:22,182 --> 00:13:26,107
<i>Efficient in both preventative measures
and tactical assault.</i>

248
00:13:26,822 --> 00:13:29,428
<i>Practical applications
include surveillance,</i>

249
00:13:29,502 --> 00:13:31,186
<i>- industrial sabotage,</i>
- (PEOPLE SCREAMING)

250
00:13:31,982 --> 00:13:36,385
<i>and the elimination of obstructions
on the road to peace.</i>

251
00:13:36,462 --> 00:13:37,702
<i>A single Yellowjacket</i>

252
