1546
01:38:43,490 --> 01:38:45,936
Cassie! I'm coming!

1547
01:38:46,970 --> 01:38:47,971
(SCREAMING)

1548
01:38:56,930 --> 01:38:58,375
(ALL GASP)

1549
01:38:58,730 --> 01:39:00,380
That's a messed-up looking dog.

1550
01:39:00,450 --> 01:39:01,576
I'm gonna destroy

1551
01:39:01,650 --> 01:39:03,220
