1697
01:47:23,929 --> 01:47:26,500
And? What'd he say?

1698
01:47:29,769 --> 01:47:31,214
He said, "Yes."

1699
01:49:26,288 --> 01:49:28,575
There's something I want to show you.

1700
01:49:30,768 --> 01:49:34,056
I realized you can't destroy power.

1701
01:49:35,728 --> 01:49:39,653
All you can do is make sure
that it's in the right hands.

1702
01:49:46,368 --> 01:49:48,496
This is an advanced prototype

1703
01:49:48,568 --> 01:49:51,458
