worked on together.

1704
01:49:52,848 --> 01:49:55,579
She never got to use it.

1705
01:49:56,208 --> 01:50:00,611
But now I realize that we were...
We were working on it for you.

1706
01:50:07,248 --> 01:50:09,774
Maybe it's time we finished it.

1707
01:50:16,408 --> 01:50:18,809
It's about damn time.

1708
01:56:19,127 --> 01:56:20,538
FALCON: <i>Hey, Cap!</i>

1709
01:56:33,727 --> 01:56:37,254
